<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>BDM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/prerequisite.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
    <script src="index.js" defer></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <div class="nav-container">
        <div class="logo-container">
          <div class="logo"></div>
          <h1>Blood Care</h1>
        </div>
        <ul class="primary-nav-items">
          <li><a href="/userlogin"><button>Log In</button></a></li>
          <li><a href="/usersignup"><button data-type="inverted" >Register</button></a></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mobile-nav-toggle" aria-controls="primary-nav" aria-expanded="false">
          <svg class="icon">
            <use xlink:href="icons/hamburger.svg#hamburger"></use>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>
    <main>
      <section class="home">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="even-columns">
            <div class="hero-text-container">
              <div class="hero-text">
                <h2 class="hero-img-text">Donate BLOOD</h2>
                <h2 class="hero-img-text" data-type="inverted">Save Lives</h2>
                <h4>Become a donor or request for blood And help save lives</h4>
                <a href="/usersignup"><button>Register as a Donor</button></a>
              </div>
          </div>
            <div class="hero-img-container">
              <img src="images/logo.png" alt="hero-image" class="hero-img">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section id="about-us">
        <div class="about">
            <h2 class="heading">What is this all about ?</h2> <br>
            <p class="head-des" class="text">We solve the problem of blood emergencies by connecting <span
                    class="one-line"><br></span> blood donors directly with blood banks in blood need. </p>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/drop.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>What we do ?</h3>
                    <p>We connect blood donors and recipients with blood banks, without any intermediary organizatons such as blood agencies, for an
                      efficient and seamless process and to avoid any delay.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/innovation.png">
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <h3>Innovative</h3>
                    <p>Blood Care is an innovative approach to address global health.We provide <span>immediate
                            access and contacts</span> to blood banks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/netwotk.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Network</h3>
                    <p>Blood Care, currently a mini-project, could be one of several community organizations in future, working to
                        respond to emergencies in an efficient manner.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/noti.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Get notified</h3>
                    <p>Blood Care is made to connect network partners with blood donors and recipients through a web based solution.
                      This will increase the ease-of-use and ease-of-access with fast and efficient solution of the blood-shortage problem. 
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/cost.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Totally Free</h3>
                    <p>Blood Care's ultimate goal is to provide an easy-to-use, easy-to-access, fast, efficient,
                        and reliable way to donate life-saving blood and get access to it, totally <span>Free of cost.</span></p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-col">
                    <div class="image">
                        <img src="./images/save.png">
                    </div>
                    <h3>Save Life</h3>
                    <p>Blood care is a DBMS Mini-Project aiming at saving lives and our main objective is to make sure that everything is done
                        to protect vulnerable persons.<span>Help
                            us by donating or refering as much as possible</span></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    {{#if result}}
    <section>
      <div></div>
      <div class="user-container" id="vol-sect">
          <ul class="volunt container">
              {{#each result}}
              <form class="vol">
                  <span class=" vol-i index">{{inc @index}}</span>
                  <span class=" vol-i number">{{this.Name}}</span>
                  <span class=" vol-i blood-group">{{this.Bgroup}}<i class="fa fa-tint" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
              </form>
              {{/each}}
          </ul>
      </div>
    </section>
    {{/if}}
    <section id="blood-banks">
      <div class="container blood-banks">
        <div class="blood-bank-text"><h2>For Blood Banks.</h2></div>
        <div class="even-columns">
          <div class="login-register">
            <div class="card">
              <img src="./images/netwotk.png" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Blood Bank</h5>
                <p class="card-text" >Some quick example text to build on the card title and make up the bulk of the card's content.</p>
                <a href="/bloodbanklogin" class="btn" >Log In</a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            
