              <a href="/bloodbanklogin"><button class="button1">Login</button></a>
            </div> --}}
          </div>
          <div class="blood-care-img"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <div class="footer-content">
          <h2>JOIN OUR CAUSE</h2>
          <p>Donating blood or platelets can be intimidating and even scary. Time to put those hesitations
              and
              fears
              aside. Learn from Blood Care and platelet donors how simple and easy it is to roll up a
              sleeve
              and help
              save lives.</p>
